{"tid":1439590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派前線 做少咗一樣好重要嘅嘢——嗌口號","createTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:24:24.000Z","uid":151168,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9feb25b6c0c87f6a4651b9047fdcd01b95a4708b","tid":1439590,"uid":151168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"首先，前線就同打仗一樣，口號可以加強軍心同士氣，清楚自己嘅目標（唔好錯重點）同嚇窒對方。<br />\n<br />\n另外，最重要係要畀人清楚知道你嘅目標。<br />\n因為而家政府不停分化我哋，話勇武只係一班純粹搞事份子，並唔係發表訴求。<br />\n令到班無腦嘅人都覺得勇武幫唔到件事發展。<br />\n<br />\n所以勇武同前線記得做每樣行動之前，無論係包圍定打柒班白衫佬。<br />\n都一定要嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n畀人清楚知道大家嘅目的，並唔係衝擊，只係表達訴求。尤其係面對警察清場，走之前都要記得嗌口號。<br />\n<br />\n畀啲例子大家睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U2XGZD5P3sc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU2XGZD5P3sc&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=686713d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U2XGZD5P3sc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWakanda Forever<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">嗌口號係無時無刻都要做</span>"},{"pid":"9d1b20147b5781398aad559416f544583eeef940","tid":1439590,"uid":151168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"783baaf493d496270111ee44d4f062eb87f75fdf","tid":1439590,"uid":151168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d2103ae397379a85994b8c7e4dcf02926ac51804","tid":1439590,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a358d211342af6c0e98ae7fc5a93a61abb117c15","tid":1439590,"uid":151168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"78a382684ca2a8fce3dc93f38696da7d6a85354b","tid":1439590,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08